Subject: [PATCH 07/14] PTP: Add support for Intel PMC Timed GPIO Controller

Add a driver supporting Intel Timed GPIO controller available as part
of some Intel PMCs.

Signed-off-by: Felipe Balbi <felipe.balbi@linux.intel.com>
